name: Ruined Makeup
description:
This is Ruined Makeup - LoRA.

It works normally with other LoRa models, but you may need to reduce the model's influence through experimentation. I suggest trying a value of 0.8 or lower.

Instructions:

To ensure a calm approach and avoid deleting this LoRa too quickly without giving it a fair chance, it's best to start with the provided example pictures and modify the tags. You can also access information about these LoRa tags and experiment with them.

If you'd like me to create a specific LoRa, please leave your comments or contact me via email.

If you want me to create some Lora then leave some comments or write me an email. You can find it at https://ko-fi.com/aitim

Like if you like it, or dislike it if you want:)

Also If you like this model you can give me a tip https://ko-fi.com/aitime

or not ^_^
